Models:

UserProfile:
-username
-age
-mobile
-email
-description

User:
-profile // OneToOne(UserProfile)
-contacts - пока хз как реализовать это, но видимо ManyToMany на самого себя)

ChatProfile:
-chat_name
-description
-count_users

Chat:
-chat_profile
-type
-creator //ForeignKey(User)
-members //ManyToMany(User)

Message:
-chat //ForeignKey(Chat)
-author //ForeignKey(User)
-content
-pub_date
-is_readed